I warned youI told you not to see him, Janet.
You are now sorry for it.
Nono! I must have known-it, and better as it is
better, better as it is, to know it all,there is no
second
strokeno other that can now be felt, except
God of Heaven! have mercy, and save me from that!'
She buried her face in the bosom of Rose, and
